<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="seize-vt">seize <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /siːz/    美 /siːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-grab">1.★ <strong>抓住 (grab)；逮捕：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>seize sb by the arm 
抓住某人的胳膊</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>seize a thief 
抓小偷</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>夺取：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>seize power</strong> 
夺权</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>抓住；把握 (时机等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I will <strong>seize</strong> the golden <strong>chance</strong> to go abroad. 
我会抓住这次绝好的机会出国。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="seize-on-upon">seize on / upon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>抓住 (可利用的事物)；突然对…大为关注：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bob seized on the rain as an excuse for missing school. 
鲍勃以下雨为借口不去上学。</p></div></div>